text: Nora Yeghyan (; born 21 April 1999) is an Armenian footballer who plays as a forward for FC Alashkert and the Armenia women's national team. ==International career== Yeghyan capped for Armenia at senior level in a 0–1 friendly loss to Lithuania on 4 March 2020. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Armenian women's footballers Category:Armenia women's international footballers Category:FC Alashkert players
